---
// Main page
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import FAQ from '../components/FAQ.astro';
import {
  ChartLine,
  Database,
  MagnifyingGlass,
  Gear,
  CheckCircle,
  ChartBar,
  Cloud,
  TrendUp,
  ShareNetwork,
  WarningCircle,
  Lightbulb,
} from '@phosphor-icons/react';
import CTA from '../components/CTA.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <main>
    <Hero />

    <section class="section problem">
      <h2 class="text-4xl">Business is booming, but where to from here?</h2>
      <p>
        Growth is exciting - but it brings new challenges. As demand increases, the systems and
        tools that worked before can start to fall behind. Here's what that often looks like:
      </p>
      <div class="problem-grid">
        <div class="problem-card">
          <div class="problem-icon">
            <TrendUp weight="duotone" size={48} />
          </div>
          <p>Customer demand is growing, but your systems aren't keeping up with the load</p>
        </div>
        <div class="problem-card">
          <div class="problem-icon">
            <ShareNetwork weight="duotone" size={48} />
          </div>
          <p>Every new product or team change adds complexity to your setup</p>
        </div>
        <div class="problem-card">
          <div class="problem-icon">
            <WarningCircle weight="duotone" size={48} />
          </div>
          <p>Technical debt is building, and you're not sure what to fix first</p>
        </div>
        <div class="problem-card">
          <div class="problem-icon">
            <Lightbulb weight="duotone" size={48} />
          </div>
          <p>You're unsure which tools, platforms, or architecture to bet on next</p>
        </div>
        <div class="problem-card">
          <div class="problem-icon">
            <Database weight="duotone" size={48} />
          </div>
          <p>You have more data than ever - but no clear way to use it to make decisions</p>
        </div>
        <div class="problem-card">
          <div class="problem-icon">
            <ChartBar weight="duotone" size={48} />
          </div>
          <p>Dashboards, reports, and tools are inconsistent - or missing altogether</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section introduction">
      <h2 class="text-4xl">Building large-scale systems at every level for over a decade</h2>
      <p>
        Hi, I'm <strong>Hendrik Crause</strong>. For the past 10+ years, I've worked on systems
        that:
      </p>
      <ul class="experience-list">
        <li>Scrape and structure web-scale data</li>
        <li>Process billions of records every day</li>
        <li>Run complex analytics across diverse datasets</li>
        <li>Pre-process data for machine learning pipelines</li>
        <li>Support production-grade web applications</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        Whether it's scaling infrastructure, building data pipelines, or turning raw data into
        business insight - I've likely solved something similar before.
      </p>
      <p>
        I started <strong>HC Scaling Solutions</strong> to help fast-moving startups build a solid foundation
        for growth. The goal is simple: apply deep technical experience to make sure your business is
        ready for what's next - without the growing pains.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section services">
      <h2 class="text-4xl">Services</h2>
      <p>
        These are just a few types of systems I can design and build, customised to your business'
        scale and needs.
      </p>
      <div class="services-grid">
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <Database weight="duotone" size={48} />
          </div>
          <h3>Data Processing Pipelines</h3>
          <p>
            Build robust data pipelines that can handle your growing data volumes and processing
            needs.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <Cloud weight="duotone" size={48} />
          </div>
          <h3>Distributed Storage Solutions</h3>
          <p>Efficiently store and manage large datasets across distributed systems.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <ChartBar weight="duotone" size={48} />
          </div>
          <h3>Custom Dashboards</h3>
          <p>
            Create intuitive dashboards that provide real-time insights into your business metrics.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <ChartLine weight="duotone" size={48} />
          </div>
          <h3>Actionable insights</h3>
          <p>Turn your data into actionable business intelligence and strategic recommendations.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section process">
      <h2 class="text-4xl">What to expect</h2>
      <div class="process-grid">
        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="step-number">1</div>
          <div class="step-icon">
            <MagnifyingGlass weight="duotone" size={48} />
          </div>
          <h3>Schedule a discovery call</h3>
          <p>
            We’ll work on a personalised scaling plan and a breakdown of how to go from where you
            are to where you’re going
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="step-number">2</div>
          <div class="step-icon">
            <Gear weight="duotone" size={48} />
          </div>
          <h3>Implementation starts</h3>
          <p>
            We get to work setting up all the needed infrastructure and build all the required
            pieces.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="step-number">3</div>
          <div class="step-icon">
            <CheckCircle weight="duotone" size={48} />
          </div>
          <h3>Your business is ready to scale</h3>
          <p>
            Use the new insights to make the right business decisions and sleep easy knowing that
            your new systems will handle the increased load.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <FAQ />
    </section>
    <section class="section" id="">
      <CTA />
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <p class="footer-text">Copyright © 2025 HC Scaling Solutions. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>
</Layout>

<style>
  .section {
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--text-color), var(--color-bright-accent));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }

  .section p {
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text-color);
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .two-column {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .image-column {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .image-placeholder {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 4/3;
    background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--bg-color), var(--hover-color));
    border-radius: 1rem;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    color: var(--text-color);
    opacity: 0.5;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  .services {
    max-width: 1200px;
  }

  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .service-card {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--bg-color), var(--hover-color));
    border-radius: 1rem;
    transition: transform 0.2s;
  }

  .service-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
  }

  .service-icon {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--star-color);
  }

  .service-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-color);
  }

  .service-card p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--text-color);
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .section {
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .section h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .two-column {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .image-placeholder {
      aspect-ratio: 16/9;
    }

    .services-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .service-card {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .problem-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .problem-card {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
  }

  .process-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .process-grid::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 48px;
    left: 15%;
    right: 15%;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--star-color);
    opacity: 0.2;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .process-step {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--bg-color), var(--hover-color));
    border-radius: 1rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    min-height: 220px;
  }

  .step-number {
    position: absolute;
    top: -20px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    background: var(--star-color);
    color: var(--bg-color);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  .step-icon {
    margin: 1rem 0 1.5rem;
    color: var(--star-color);
  }

  .process-step h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    min-height: 4.5rem;
    color: var(--text-color);
  }

  .process-step p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--text-color);
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .process-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .process-grid::before {
      display: none;
    }

    .process-step {
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    }
  }

  .problem {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .problem-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .problem-card {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--bg-color), var(--hover-color));
    border-radius: 1rem;
    transition: transform 0.2s;
  }

  .problem-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
  }

  .problem-icon {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--star-color);
  }

  .problem-card p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--text-color);
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .introduction {
    text-align: left;
  }

  .experience-list {
    list-style: disc;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .experience-list li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--text-color);
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .footer-text {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--text-color);
    opacity: 0.5;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
</style>
